{
  *****************************************************************************

   Rivest-Shamir-Adleman (RSA) Public-Key Cryptography
    - RSA Oriented Big-Integer Computation
    - RSA Low-Level Cryptography Functions
    - Registration of our RSA Engine to the TCryptAsym Factory

